content:
Match agents to shifts with ease. Create shifts from templates or a capacity plan. Then set up scheduling rules, constraints, and objectives so that your planners can use the scheduling tools—get candidates, batch assign, and mass shift update—to assign agents to shifts.

Workforce Engagement is available in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions
Shift Scheduling is available in the Contact Center SKU, Einstein 1 Service Edition, and Service Suites

Manage Shift Scheduling
Create Shifts in Bulk from a Capacity Plan
title: Service Cloud Agent Scheduling
